criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosed type 2 diabetes for diabetic groups according to WHO (1999) diagnostic
             criteria;

          -  BMI≥24 for obese/overweight groups;

          -  Aged between 50 and 70 years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  TG≥4.56 mmol/L;

          -  Proliferative retinopathy;

          -  Pregnancy or lactation;

          -  Allergy to fish;

          -  Taking insulin;

          -  Premenopausal or menopause within 6 months;

          -  Have participated in other clinical trials in the last three months.
